<item>
            <title>[LU-10984] &#8216;lfs setstripe&#8217; fails with &#8220;lfs setstripe: error on ioctl 0x8008669a for &apos;*&#8217; (3): Invalid argument&#8221;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10984</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#8216;lfs setstripe&#8217; fails with &#8220;lfs setstripe: error on ioctl 0x8008669a for &apos;*&#8217; (3): Invalid argument&#8221;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at the test logs at &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c94d8e38-415b-11e8-960d-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c94d8e38-415b-11e8-960d-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;, we see several sanity tests fail on &#8216;lfs setstripe&#8217; for PPC architecture. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity test_27a, 27b, 27d, 27e, 27k, 27r, 27w, 27wa, 27z, 27C, 27E, 56t, 56u, 56x, 56xa, 56xb, 65k, 78, 101b, &#8230; all fail with similar errors. From the client test_log, we see&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 27e: setstripe existing file (should return error) ==================================== 05:40:03 (1523857203)
CMD: trevis-22vm2 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n version 2&amp;gt;/dev/null ||
				/usr/sbin/lctl lustre_build_version 2&amp;gt;/dev/null ||
				/usr/sbin/lctl --version 2&amp;gt;/dev/null | cut -d&apos; &apos; -f2
lfs setstripe: error on ioctl 0x8008669a for &apos;/mnt/lustre/d27e.sanity/f27e.sanity&apos; (3): Invalid argument
 sanity test_27e: @@@@@@ FAIL: setstripe failed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Log for other failures are at&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c94d8e38-415b-11e8-960d-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c94d8e38-415b-11e8-960d-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/82aab230-44c1-11e8-b45c-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/82aab230-44c1-11e8-b45c-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
